snippet.title: Jason Aldean - Drowns the Whiskey (Official Music Video) ft. Miranda Lambert
snippet.description:
Check out the official music video for "Drowns the Whiskey" by Jason Aldean ft. Miranda Lambert featured on his album Rearview Town.  https://jasonaldean.lnk.to/rearviewtown

►Subscribe to Jason's Official YouTube Channel: https://JasonAldean.lnk.to/ytchannel

►To see all upcoming tour dates, visit: https://www.jasonaldean.com

Lyrics:
ALL THE FOLKS DOWN IN LYNCHBURG TENNESSEE
BEEN WORKIN’ HARD FOR GOOD OL’ BOYS LIKE ME
I DON’T WANNA BE THE ONE TO TELL ‘EM
THAT STUFF THAT THEY BEEN SELLIN’
AIN’T WORKIN’ LIKE IT SHOULD
BUT I DAMN SURE WISH IT WOULD

WHISKEY’S SUPPOSED TO DROWN A MEMORY
I’VE GONE FROM ONE TO ONE TOO MANY
AND THE THING THAT REALLY GETS ME
IS HOW YOUR MEMORY DROWNS THE WHISKEY

MAYBE IT’S THE BAR OR THIS STOOL I’M ON
MAYBE IT’S THE BAND AND THIS SAD OL’ SONG
THAT KEEPS ME BUYIN’ ROUNDS
KEEPS ME TURNIN’ DOWN
ANY GIRL THAT WANTS TO DANCE
YOU AIN’T GIVIN’ THEM A CHANCE

WHISKEY’S SUPPOSED TO DROWN THE MEMORY
I’VE GONE FROM ONE TO ONE TOO MANY
AND THE THING THAT REALLY GETS ME
IS HOW YOUR MEMORY DROWNS THE WHISKEY

GIRL I’M LIVIN’ PROOF THAT 80 PROOF
AIN’T GOT A SHOT AT TOUCHIN’ YOU

WHISKEY’S SUPPOSED TO DROWN A MEMORY
I’VE GONE FROM ONE TO ONE TOO MANY
AND THE THING THAT REALLY GETS ME

IS WHISKEY’S SUPPOSED TO DROWN THE MEMORY
I’VE GONE FROM ONE TO ONE TOO MANY
AND THE THING THAT REALLY GETS ME
IS HOW YOUR MEMORY DROWNS THE WHISKEY

YEAH THE THING THAT REALLY GETS ME
IS HOW YOUR MEMORY DROWNS THE WHISKEY

ALL THE FOLKS DOWN IN LYNCHBURG TENNESSEE
BEEN WORKIN’ HARD FOR GOOD OL’ BOYS LIKE ME 

Written By: Josh Thompson Jeff Middleton, Brandon Kinney
